1
00:00:57,680 --> 00:00:58,850
Strike!

2
00:01:00,970 --> 00:01:01,510
Well done!

3
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,520
Nice ball!

4
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:14,940
Strike!

5
00:01:17,990 --> 00:01:18,700
Strike!

6
00:01:18,990 --> 00:01:20,160
Nice ball!

7
00:01:20,660 --> 00:01:21,330
Woo-jin,

8
00:01:21,620 --> 00:01:22,620
your follow-through is better now.

9
00:01:22,910 --> 00:01:23,500
What was the speed?
Well.

10
00:01:24,250 --> 00:01:24,790
Um.

11
00:01:25,210 --> 00:01:25,960
155 km/h.

12
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,790
That's faster than before.

13
00:01:28,210 --> 00:01:30,290
I just can't let it go.

14
00:01:30,630 --> 00:01:31,590
He used to be MVP in Middle school.

15
00:01:32,090 --> 00:01:33,590
How come everything just vanished?

16
00:01:34,090 --> 00:01:34,760
Put him in.

17
00:01:35,550 --> 00:01:36,130
Jeong-ho,

18
00:01:36,970 --> 00:01:37,380
get ready.

19
00:01:55,030 --> 00:01:56,150
You bastard!
You did that on purpose!

20
00:01:56,190 --> 00:01:56,650
Say it!

21
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:57,700
You did it on purpose!

22
00:01:58,530 --> 00:02:00,570
Who are you trying
to take out today?

23
00:02:02,530 --> 00:02:03,950
Try taking me out.

24
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:09,040
Just like I practiced.

25
00:02:26,890 --> 00:02:27,770
Damn it!

26
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:28,640
Ball!

27
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:33,520
Shit.

28
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,280
Woo-jin,

29
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:37,690
relax.

30
00:02:38,070 --> 00:02:39,320
Take it easy, nice and slow.

31
00:02:42,660 --> 00:02:43,740
Two balls.

32
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:50,210
Come on!

33
00:02:50,620 --> 00:02:51,330
Three balls.

34
00:02:51,830 --> 00:02:52,790
Just give up!

35
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:54,040
Woo-jin,

36
00:02:54,170 --> 00:02:55,090
let's try again.

37
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:29,660
I'm a pitcher

38
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:33,170
who can't throw strikes.

39
00:04:03,660 --> 00:04:06,490
I'll practice until I can throw strikes with my eyes closed.

40
00:04:49,990 --> 00:04:51,120
Wow!

41
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:52,750
Home run!

42
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,120
What the hell!

43
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:02,800
Who are you?

44
00:05:06,090 --> 00:05:06,470
Me?

45
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:07,550
Yeah, you.

46
00:05:11,310 --> 00:05:12,310
Interesting.

47
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:13,350
What's interesting?

48
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:15,440
I won't tell you.

49
00:05:16,590 --> 00:05:16,980
Never mind.

50
00:05:17,020 --> 00:05:18,940
Why are you here if you're not a club member?

51
00:05:19,110 --> 00:05:20,060
I came to see you.

52
00:05:20,570 --> 00:05:20,900
Me?
Me?

53
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:22,070
Yeah, you.

54
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,360
Why do you want to see me?

55
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,780
You wanna know? Strike me out.

56
00:05:29,740 --> 00:05:30,530
What?

57
00:05:30,910 --> 00:05:31,830
You don't think you can?

58
00:05:33,990 --> 00:05:35,190
Alright! Play ball!

59
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:42,750
So you wanna play?

60
00:05:47,550 --> 00:05:49,300
Just pitch on muscle memory.

61
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:00,810
Ouch!

62
00:06:03,570 --> 00:06:04,070
Hey!

63
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:06,190
Damn it! Hey!

64
00:06:06,740 --> 00:06:07,400
Hey!

65
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:10,650
Are you okay?

66
00:06:10,990 --> 00:06:11,870
Damn it!

67
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:13,830
Hello?
Seriously?

68
00:06:14,410 --> 00:06:14,740
Damn.

69
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:16,330
That really hurts.

70
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:18,210
What?

71
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:20,540
But I can take it.

72
00:06:21,710 --> 00:06:22,880
Are you kidding me?

73
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:24,550
Damn it.

74
00:06:24,710 --> 00:06:26,260
Hey, of all times,

75
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:27,470
you pull a joke like this?

76
00:06:27,510 --> 00:06:29,220
But that really hurts.

77
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,010
I don't wanna see you again.

78
00:06:33,050 --> 00:06:34,760
But I got hit!

79
00:06:36,890 --> 00:06:37,480
Hey!

80
00:06:45,530 --> 00:06:47,070
That was a good pitch.

81
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,700
This is ridiculous.

82
00:06:52,370 --> 00:06:52,870
Hey,

83
00:06:53,370 --> 00:06:54,830
you hit me, why are you mad?

84
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,620
I should be the one mad.

85
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,660
You're being so unreasonable.

86
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,960
Do you know how
powerful your pitch is?

87
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,330
Of course, you don't.

88
00:07:02,380 --> 00:07:03,790
You've never been hit by one.

89
00:07:04,290 --> 00:07:05,420
The moment I get hit,

90
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:07,710
everything went blurry,
I literally saw stars.

91
00:07:08,010 --> 00:07:08,550
You get it?

92
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:10,010
Hey,

93
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:11,840
are you just gonna run off like that?

94
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:16,930
Run?
Run?

95
00:07:17,970 --> 00:07:18,930
Yeah, run.

96
00:07:18,980 --> 00:07:20,640
Didn't you hear what I said?

97
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:21,690
What?

98
00:07:21,730 --> 00:07:23,560
I told you to stay away from me!

99
00:07:23,810 --> 00:07:24,230
What?

100
00:07:24,810 --> 00:07:26,860
I thought you couldn't see me.

101
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,440
You looking for a fight?

102
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:30,360
I'm being honest.

103
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:34,410
Who the hell are you?

104
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,740
You have to strike me out to find out.

105
00:07:36,910 --> 00:07:37,330
Ah.

106
00:07:37,740 --> 00:07:39,080
I'll just ignore him.

107
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:39,750
Hey!

108
00:07:39,790 --> 00:07:40,910
Wait!

109
00:07:45,130 --> 00:07:45,750
My name is Tae-hui.

110
00:07:46,460 --> 00:07:47,180
Kwon Tae-hui.
Kwon Tae-hui?

111
00:07:49,670 --> 00:07:50,840
I've never heard of you.

112
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:51,720
I just transferred here.

113
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:53,180
Oh, yeah?

114
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:54,720
Then why are you following me?

115
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:55,470
Are you a stalker?

116
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:57,100
Stalker? I'm the victim.

117
00:07:57,210 --> 00:07:57,700
Victim...

118
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,560
Do you want money?

119
00:08:00,740 --> 00:08:01,340
No.

120
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,230
That's really rude.

121
00:08:03,270 --> 00:08:05,610
Then what do you want?

122
00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:10,110
Put a patch on me.

123
00:08:10,610 --> 00:08:10,940
What?
Quick,

124
00:08:12,030 --> 00:08:13,450
put a pain relief patch on my back.

125
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:16,200
What a weirdo!

126
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,410
What do you mean?

127
00:08:18,330 --> 00:08:20,450
I just can't reach my back.

128
00:08:21,290 --> 00:08:21,830
Look.

129
00:08:21,870 --> 00:08:22,910
I can't reach.

130
00:08:23,370 --> 00:08:24,790
Total weirdo.

131
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:26,960
Weirdo?

132
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:27,630
Hey!
Hey!

133
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:29,090
Where are you going?

134
00:08:30,590 --> 00:08:32,130
Where did I hit you?

135
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,590
Gosh...

136
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:35,680
What the hell?

137
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,760
Pull your shirt up.

138
00:08:37,300 --> 00:08:38,050
Damn it.

139
00:08:38,300 --> 00:08:39,100
Hurry up!

140
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:41,640
You told me to show you.

141
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:44,520
So sudden.

142
00:08:44,690 --> 00:08:45,350
Heart racing?

143
00:08:45,690 --> 00:08:46,400
Forget it.

144
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:48,560
Where exactly did I hit you?

145
00:08:48,610 --> 00:08:49,400
Here,

146
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:51,860
by my ribs, around the back.

147
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:52,940
See it?

148
00:08:52,990 --> 00:08:53,990
There's no bruise.

149
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:54,610
What?
No bruise?

150
00:08:55,490 --> 00:08:55,740
No.
Impossible.

151
00:08:56,700 --> 00:08:58,200
Left side or right side?

152
00:08:58,450 --> 00:08:59,830
This side.

153
00:09:10,170 --> 00:09:11,130
What are you doing?
Hey,

154
00:09:12,710 --> 00:09:14,090
it's just putting on a patch.

155
00:09:14,130 --> 00:09:15,720
Just don't think too much.

156
00:09:16,180 --> 00:09:17,050
Do you act like this
on the mound too?

157
00:09:17,260 --> 00:09:17,800
What?

158
00:09:18,260 --> 00:09:19,550
No wonder you can't throw strikes.

159
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,010
Alas.
Hey!

160
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:22,100
You don't know anything.

161
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:23,770
You weren't like this in middle school.

162
00:09:24,430 --> 00:09:24,980
Middle school?
Yeah.

163
00:09:25,730 --> 00:09:26,850
How do you know?

164
00:09:26,890 --> 00:09:28,400
I've been your fan since then.

165
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:30,150
What are you talking about?

166
00:09:31,070 --> 00:09:32,610
I've been your fan all the time.

167
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:33,320
My fan?
Come on,

168
00:09:35,070 --> 00:09:36,610
that sounds ridiculous.

169
00:09:37,110 --> 00:09:39,120
Do you know which middle school I went to?

170
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:42,160
I even remember your jersey number.

171
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,120
Hyeonsang Middle School, number 23.

172
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:46,080
19 1/3 innings pitched,

173
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,960
6 hits, 4 walks,

174
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,830
27 strikeouts, 1 run earned.

175
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:53,000
ERA 0.47. You were the National MVP,

176
00:09:53,250 --> 00:09:53,960
right?

177
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,510
You're really my fan?

178
00:09:56,550 --> 00:09:58,220
You were cool back then,

179
00:09:59,590 --> 00:10:01,350
but now you suck.

180
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:02,140
Shut up.

181
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,600
Setting that aside,

182
00:10:05,810 --> 00:10:07,100
don't you need a manager?

183
00:10:10,810 --> 00:10:11,940
No.
